thread.title_full: Cambridge Proofreading reviewed by Jonathan Garcia

author: Jonathan Garcia
title: Jonathan Garcia
text: I have used this service 3 times for various writing assignments, my latest one was edited by Sophie. I am very impressed with the level of professionalism and timeliness. Especially with Sophie's work, I expressed my time concerns and was not disappointed, I received the work quickly and professionally.This company has served me well over the years and I will definitely continue to use their service.
